  "texts": [
    "It offers user-friendly, natural language interfaces for seamless human-machine interaction.",
    "We designed the GPT-based chatbot as a prototype for implementing GenAI chatbots within small to medium-sized manufacturing environments, offering both online and offline versions of the industrial bot and ensuring adaptability to diverse factory setups (limited connectivity or security concerns).",
    "• Integrating ecosystem and human-centric metrics: The bot monitors factory parameters such as pollution levels and maximum overtime hours, ensuring compliance with Industry 5.0's dual focus on sustainability and human well-being.Our research promotes the implementation of GenAI chatbots in small-to medium-sized manufacturing enterprises in an I5.0 context by proposing the design of a GPT industrial bot that improves factory operators' daily working experience by monitoring their production and tracking human-centric parameters such as plant pollution rate and maximum overtime working hours for employees to ensure safe decision-making.",
    "Our GPT chatbot also assists workers with fault-finding tasks, root cause analysis, and synthetic data generation.",
    "It also increases workers' knowledge by generating additional tips and clues to maintain the factory based on received queries and monitored data."
  ],
